ollapses that transforms the result into\nthe nerve of some robust covering of the shape.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Apr 2013 16:50:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Nov 2015 13:48:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-16"}
