e-surface\nflows improve the behaviour at the intersection of free surface and wall as\nwell as prevent free-surface detachment when using the volume diffusion term.\nFinally, this paper is concluded by a simulation of a dam break over a wedge\ndemonstrating the improvements proposed in this paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Apr 2013 17:36:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Jun 2013 14:28:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
