es. As a consequence, the\noccurrence rate of potentially habitable planets is larger than previously\nthought.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Apr 2013 19:39:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Jul 2013 09:55:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 4 Sep 2013 21:29:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
