iagnostic diagrams presented here allow one to study\nthe properties of known PNe and to uncover objects not previously classified.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 13 Apr 2013 00:59:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-16"}
